{"tid":2457952,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"M1 Mac 新增為 iPhone / iPad app的「手掣模擬」功能，方便打機用","createTime":"2021-03-23T05:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T16:32:56.000Z","uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ada068c89a83a6a08c0a85eaa1449ec255367a29","tid":2457952,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"自去年秋季發佈以來，該公司一直在努力完善和改進iOS App在M1 Mac上的運行體驗。而近日，我們就在macOS中看到新增了以「鼠鍵模擬手掣」的功能。蘋果在macOS Big Sur 11.3的Beta測試版本中，為M1 Mac設備引入了兼容iPhone / iPad應用的「手掣模擬」功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUWjBwGMHtY1a61VWexwdAqDhUbxfgaobB6ftDrCGuVn9?filename=byBthKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyBthKu.png&h=9015cf9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，當運行iPhone / iPad應用時，macOS Big Sur 11.3最新測試版本會先打開一個「觸控替代」（Touch Alternatives）和「手掣控制」（Game Control）界面。<br />\n<br />\n手掣模擬將允許在M1 Mac 上通過鼠鍵更精準地控制 iPhone / iPad 遊戲，對於基於觸摸交互的iOS App來說，此舉可讓M1 Mac 更好地兼容遊戲App 。<br />\n<br />\n在啟用了手掣模擬（Controller Emulation）後，常用的手掣按鍵，也會預設映射到指定的鍵盤/ 滑鼠按鈕上。例如 Q &rarr; X、方向鍵&rarr; WASD、E &rarr; Y，以及可通過按住Tab / Shift &rarr; 使用L1 / L2，並用Space &rarr; A 鍵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVRzjmeVVJzfeNv2eRu5wErA8vdiTnpbwv7EivVeLPqs8?filename=O9D7yiV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9D7yiV.png&h=e403a9fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cf4b2e73d0cc72f6172f62723c4f9acc39fb65f","tid":2457952,"uid":385412,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"啫係用電腦keyboard 同 mouse 玩手機game<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f339ef468e8b03992187597650bf12a5f11f2217","tid":2457952,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T05:21:34.000Z","msg":"舊年推api俾iPad支援keyboard/mouse打機<br />\n依家到keyboard &amp; mouse可以模擬手掣<br />\n<br />\nApple知道開發跨平台gaming最大問題已經<strong><span class=\"red\">唔係效能差距</span></strong><br />\n最大障礙係操作不兼容，touch screen/keyboard mouse/controller操作差距太大，好難開發<br />\n<br />\n我以arm+metal開發一隻game支援controller<br />\nApple TV坐客廳、iPad坐床可以用controller玩<br />\nMac可以用keyboard &amp; mouse模擬手掣<br />\n<br />\n所以我冇估錯，Apple同M$諗嘅嘢係一樣<br />\n一個打通arm+metal跨平台gaming<br />\n另一個打通x86+dx12ult跨平台gaming<br />\n<br />\nBring keyboard and mouse gaming to iPad<br />\n<a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2020/10617/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.apple.com%2Fvideos%2Fplay%2Fwwdc2020%2F10617%2F&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXEkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=14901353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2020/10617/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GFYVzxpl-nA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGFYVzxpl-nA&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXEkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=43467497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GFYVzxpl-nA</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw目前touch alternatives真係好廢，希望直接引入an模擬器customize啲touchscreen掣"},{"pid":"7ce92ff6a6f835a644964f7205304f7a6bbde9bd","tid":2457952,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"我就睇下Apple個平台發展到幾大先有廠敢離大隊放3A新作入去搵真銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7252d6522fa1ddb10ff6a8d419f4900cbdf505","tid":2457952,"uid":70702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ce92ff6a6f835a644964f7205304f7a6bbde9bd","tid":2457952,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"我就睇下Apple個平台發展到幾大先有廠敢離大隊放3A新作入去搵真銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"有撚排，玩佢要直頭換埋部腦，傻撚左咩。<br />\n如